<plot>Jack Logan loses all his money in a loaded-dice craps game with a couple of strangers, who turn out to be hold-up men. In order to get his money back he sets up a deal where they can rob the "Cannonball Express," an express train on which his father, John, is the engineer. And they frames his brother Ned for the robbery.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?093049</url></doc>
